1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,780
[EP. 04] Before our Lips Touch

2
00:00:09,940 --> 00:00:11,140
So hot…

3
00:00:11,140 --> 00:00:12,860
Why is it so hot in fall?

4
00:00:12,860 --> 00:00:13,540
Oh?

5
00:00:14,120 --> 00:00:15,060
That’s Wook!

6
00:00:15,940 --> 00:00:16,440
Hey!

7
00:00:16,440 --> 00:00:17,140
You scared me!

8
00:00:17,540 --> 00:00:20,000
Let me have a sip.

9
00:00:20,240 --> 00:00:22,520
Kyaaaa! Your coffee is just the best!

10
00:00:27,560 --> 00:00:28,560
Hey,

11
00:00:28,560 --> 00:00:29,850
Are you with me?

12
00:00:29,860 --> 00:00:30,560
What? Yeah…

13
00:00:30,620 --> 00:00:32,880
Why is the weather like this in fall?

14
00:00:32,880 --> 00:00:34,040
I know…

15
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:35,680
I want my break back.

16
00:00:35,920 --> 00:00:36,740
Me, too…

17
00:00:36,940 --> 00:00:39,300
I want to skip class and go hang out
somewhere nearby.

18
00:00:39,800 --> 00:00:41,340
You, too? Should we go?

19
00:00:41,340 --> 00:00:43,370
This weather is forcing us to go have fun.

20
00:00:43,370 --> 00:00:46,860
So, you studied hard when it was cold?

21
00:00:46,870 --> 00:00:49,920
You’re not one to judge, Yeo Reum.

22
00:00:49,920 --> 00:00:51,970
At least I don’t blame the weather.

23
00:00:51,970 --> 00:00:53,820
I’m just saying…

24
00:00:54,540 --> 00:00:57,460
Argh, I really don’t want to go to class…

25
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:58,860
Gosh!

26
00:00:58,860 --> 00:00:59,920
I’m late for class!

27
00:00:59,920 --> 00:01:00,920
See you later!

28
00:01:00,920 --> 00:01:01,420
What?

29
00:01:01,780 --> 00:01:02,280
Okay…

30
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,480
One-sided love
emotion that writes the same behavior differently

31
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:45,840
What are you doing?

32
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,160
Ah… Nothing…

33
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,120
Let me have a sip.

34
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,600
It’s mine!

35
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:57,800
A Day Before Us

